    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's interesting. So if the research points to those differences in muscle fibers, does that mean there are certain sports or types of training that are basically \"hardwired\" for certain groups? Like, if I have a client from a specific background, should I be leaning more towards power/explosiveness or endurance based on those stats you mentioned?",
